154
00:10:17,683 --> 00:10:19,700
We don't know.
He took precautions

155
00:10:19,701 --> 00:10:21,519
To keep his identity
anonymous.

156
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:24,271
But for the past 12 hours, I've
been trying hard to find him,

157
00:10:24,272 --> 00:10:26,674
Because I believe that if this
man isn't already dead,

158
00:10:26,675 --> 00:10:27,958
