549
00:40:53,967 --> 00:40:55,551
[tires squealing]

550
00:41:03,894 --> 00:41:06,361
Oh, my God.
Are you all right?

551
00:41:06,362 --> 00:41:07,613
I think so.

552
00:41:07,614 --> 00:41:10,099
Take that left.
Maybe you can cut him off.

553
00:41:11,785 --> 00:41:14,237
Go!

